      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].choice.optionA.label
      value: Retry?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].choice.optionB.label
      value: Give Up
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].choice.optionA.nextIndex
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].choice.optionB.nextIndex
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Well, well, well; and who might you be?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: You seem to have a lot of pep in your step- But not a whole lot of cash
        in your pocket...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: "Oh!, but don\u2019t worry, friend. I can fix that. "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[3].text
      value: My name is Nobody- But you can call me Mr. Nobody.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: And I am here to give you the opportunity of a lifetime!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: "So let\u2019s make a deal, shall we?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: "I just so happen to own a casino. A very\u2026 special casino."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[7].text
      value: 'One that you can enter, but not leave. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[8].text
      value: "Not until you reach Salvation. Or, well, unless you burn through all
        your cash first, of course\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[9].text
      value: "Salvation is the promise of a new life. A new beginning. A new body,
        a new face, a new name\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].choice.optionA.nextIndex
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].choice.optionB.nextIndex
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: "Haha, you\u2019ve made the right choice tonight, gambler!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: "After all, you\u2019ve got nothing to lose\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: "Now step right up into my parlor! Welcome to Nobody\u2019s Casino!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[3].text
      value: My name is Nobody- But you can call me Mr. Nobody.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: And I am here to give you the opportunity of a lifetime!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: "So let\u2019s make a deal, shall we?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: "I just so happen to own a casino. A very\u2026 special casino."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[7].text
      value: "Not until you reach Salvation. Or, well, unless you burn through all
        your cash first, of course\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[8].text
      value: "Salvation is the promise of a new life. A new beginning. A new body,
        a new face, a new name\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[9].text
      value: "Salvation is the promise of a new life. A new beginning. A new body,
        a new face, a new name\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: "Ah\u2026 Now that\u2019s\u2026 Surprising. Really, it caught me off-guard."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: I thought I had ya.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: "But oh well, I\u2019m not pushy. Your choice is your choice."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[3].text
      value: Turn around and step back into the dark now. I wish you the best, buddy.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: I really do.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: After having wandered through the dirty streets for days on end with
        no shelter, no food and barely any water,; your body eventually gave up.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: As you expire, you spend your last moments wondering where it all went
        wrong. What you could have done to change this outcome.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[7].text
      value: THE END
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[10].text
      value: A new purpose.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[11].text
      value: "As for the funds\u2026 Don\u2019t worry, I\u2019ll toss a coin or two
        your way, maybe a hundred; so you can get started right away."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[12].text
      value: So, whaddya say, gambler? Do we have a deal? Are you ready to win a
        new life?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[10].text
      value: A new purpose.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[11].text
      value: "As for the funds\u2026 Don\u2019t worry, I\u2019ll toss a coin or two
        your way, maybe a hundred; so you can get started right away."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
